{"tid":765964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被粗大茄子插入直腸　男子：走在田裡不小心滑倒","createTime":"2018-08-03T08:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T04:14:39.000Z","uid":75969,"like":292,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"54b15df6828ee2491a613f23b3188c5fc0fe879b","tid":765964,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:07:36.000Z","msg":"大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n大陸一名男子日前因「直腸卡茄子」而就醫，他向醫師聲稱，自己經過一處茄子田時滑倒，意外被地上的茄子插入直腸，拖了19小時才就醫。結果第一家醫院還無法為他取出，只好將他轉院，而茄子在男子的直腸內待了一天半的時間，才由第二家醫院取出來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/08/01/1470815-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F1470815-XXL.jpg&h=8ec3aee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲從男子直腸取出的茄子。（圖／翻攝自微博）</span><br />\n<br />\n根據陸媒報導，男子就醫時表示，他於7月24日晚上10時多經過茄子田時，不小心滑了一大跤，當下屁股著地，被田裡的茄子插進直腸內，挖了半天也挖不出來，拖了19小時才就醫。<br />\n<br />\n男子就醫後，連醫師都束手無策，只好幫他轉院到第二間醫院，交由專業的外科醫師處理，拖到了26日凌晨，這根茄子才終於從直腸內取出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/08/01/1470814-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F1470814-XXL.jpg&h=1566e286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲男子直腸內卡著肥大的茄子。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n儘管醫師相信男子是因跌倒而被插入的，但網友根本不相信，紛紛留言嘲諷「真會鬼扯」、「原來有特殊茄子是朝上而不是垂掛」、「何時挖竹筍？」、「希望他老兄下次經過冬瓜田時要小心點啊」、「哪個品牌的褲子這麼脆弱？」、「太噁了吧&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=410843\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D410843&d=ubKrzgiQmVzJPhp33jvs0jPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=7325ed88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D410843&h=31adfa39\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=410843</a>"},{"pid":"6e30b46cbfcc94d532fde354f295f397a28658ac","tid":765964,"uid":75969,"like":425,"dislike":2,"score":423,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:07:40.000Z","msg":"咁大碌都插得入 肯定俾人開發過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0689c85e75efa385254b4a5631d1b9be911d6f2","tid":765964,"uid":25099,"like":130,"dislike":3,"score":127,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:11:10.000Z","msg":"唔洗落咸魚, <br />\n直接切開炒,"},{"pid":"5bb6c3e2a2f23c020ebaf8c899902f3e347b50de","tid":765964,"uid":25099,"like":460,"dislike":7,"score":453,"quote":{"pid":"c0689c85e75efa385254b4a5631d1b9be911d6f2","tid":765964,"uid":25099,"like":130,"dislike":3,"score":127,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:11:10.000Z","msg":"唔洗落咸魚, <br />\n直接切開炒,"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static3.orstatic.com/userphoto/photo/3/2TH/00K1KX4D8D2F8FF1F6A2AAl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic3.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto%2Fphoto%2F3%2F2TH%2F00K1KX4D8D2F8FF1F6A2AAl.jpg&h=c673f88b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3469beda2788504905e5e8ed84c2ceaf2273d70d","tid":765964,"uid":9466,"like":98,"dislike":2,"score":96,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:13:43.000Z","msg":"不小心插入系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad488d61c020786ead1cd8b1871c8df6495e8eb4","tid":765964,"uid":15,"like":345,"dislike":2,"score":343,"quote":{"pid":"6e30b46cbfcc94d532fde354f295f397a28658ac","tid":765964,"uid":75969,"like":425,"dislike":2,"score":423,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:07:40.000Z","msg":"咁大碌都插得入 肯定俾人開發過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/162304_db6757dd6e3013dba3e0bfff9f25717c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F162304_db6757dd6e3013dba3e0bfff9f25717c.png&h=d8020326&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3250d78f1875d58ed131cbb8000c3fb7488a4b3","tid":765964,"uid":176447,"like":386,"dislike":1,"score":385